## 2. Current baseline (our app)

### 2.1 Tool count: **15**

| # | Route | Tool |
|---|-------|------|
| 1 | `/` | Main Picker Wheel |
| 2 | `/team-picker` | Team Picker |
| 3 | `/yes-no-picker-wheel` | Yes / No Picker |
| 4 | `/number-picker-wheel` | Number Picker |
| 5 | `/letter-picker-wheel` | Letter Picker |
| 6 | `/country-wheel` | Country Picker |
| 7 | `/state-wheel` | State Picker |
| 8 | `/color-picker-wheel` | Color Picker |
| 9 | `/image-picker-wheel` | Image Picker |
| 10 | `/date-picker-wheel` | Date Picker |
| 11 | `/mlb-wheel` | MLB Team Picker |
| 12 | `/nba-wheel` | NBA Team Picker |
| 13 | `/fortnite-wheel` | Fortnite Skin Picker |
| 14 | `/pokemon-wheel` | Pokémon Picker |
| 15 | `/lol-wheel` | League of Legends Champion Picker |

### 2.2 Strengths today

- 15 specialized tools — same count as PickerWheel.com
- AI on homepage, MLB, NBA, Fortnite, Pokémon (real `/api/ai` where wired)
- Game modes: bingo, memory, collection race, sequence match, roulette, speed, combo, precision
- Gamification: achievements, themes, analytics, social hub (partial)
- Multi-wheel manager (localStorage via Zustand)

### 2.3 Known gaps today

- Share button in header — no handler
- API routes (`/api/settings`, `/api/wheel-manager`, `/api/tools/*`) — stubs only
- Persistence — browser localStorage only, no accounts
- No public wheel library / SEO template pages
- No embed widget, no PWA install flow
- Several “AI” tools are simulated (yes/no, date, country, state, letter, team chat, LoL)
- Missing tools vs PickerWheel: Instagram Comment Picker, NFL, Flag Quiz
- Missing action mode vs PickerWheel: **Accumulation** (count builds across spins)
- Footer links (coin flip, dice, help, FAQ) — placeholder `#`

