## 3. Competitor tool comparison

### 3.1 Tool counts

| Platform | Dedicated tools | Extra products |
|----------|-----------------|----------------|
| **Our app** | **15** | Game modes, AI hub |
| **PickerWheel.com** | **15** | Embed widget, FlipSimu coin flipper |
| **SpinTheWheel.app** | **1** (generic wheel) | Thousands of community wheels, Android/iOS apps, Discord bot |

### 3.2 PickerWheel.com — full tool list (15)

1. Main Picker Wheel  
2. Team Picker Wheel  
3. Yes No Picker Wheel  
4. Number Picker Wheel  
5. Letter Picker Wheel  
6. Country Picker Wheel  
7. State Picker Wheel  
8. Color Picker Wheel  
9. Image Picker Wheel  
10. Date Picker Wheel  
11. Instagram Comment Picker Wheel  
12. MLB Picker Wheel  
13. NBA Picker Wheel  
14. NFL Picker Wheel  
15. Flag Quiz Picker Wheel  

### 3.3 Overlap matrix (us vs PickerWheel.com)

| Tool | Us | PickerWheel | Notes |
|------|:--:|:-----------:|-------|
| Main picker | ✅ | ✅ | They lead on share/collect, CSV, weights/labels/colors |
| Team picker | ✅ | ✅ | We have CSV + simulated Gemini chat |
| Yes/No | ✅ | ✅ | |
| Number | ✅ | ✅ | |
| Letter | ✅ | ✅ | We have challenge modes |
| Country | ✅ | ✅ | |
| State | ✅ | ✅ | |
| Color | ✅ | ✅ | |
| Image | ✅ | ✅ | |
| Date | ✅ | ✅ | |
| MLB | ✅ | ✅ | We have deeper AI |
| NBA | ✅ | ✅ | We have deeper AI |
| Fortnite | ✅ | ❌ | **Our unique** |
| Pokémon | ✅ | ❌ | **Our unique** |
| LoL | ✅ | ❌ | **Our unique** |
| Instagram Comment | ❌ | ✅ | **Their unique** — giveaway / influencer use case |
| NFL | ❌ | ✅ | **Their unique** — easy clone from MLB/NBA |
| Flag Quiz | ❌ | ✅ | **Their unique** — quiz, not just spin |

**Net:** 15 vs 15 — 12 shared, 3 unique each.

### 3.4 SpinTheWheel.app — strategy (not tool count)

- Single wheel editor: labels, colors, sounds, share
- Growth via **community wheel library** (trending, categories, SEO pages)
- Mobile apps + Discord bot
- Not competing on specialized tools — competing on discovery and distribution

