## 5. Suggested phases (draft — override in §1)

> **Do not treat this as final.** Reorder after you fill §1.

### Phase 0 — Quick wins
- F-26 Ctrl+Enter on homepage  
- F-23 Mystery result  
- Header Share handler (minimum: copy link / export JSON)  
- T-01 NFL wheel  

### Phase 1 — Retention core
- F-01 Shareable wheel links  
- F-12 Real API persistence OR F-10 accounts + F-11 cloud save  
- F-20 CSV import  
- F-22 Accumulation mode  

### Phase 2 — Growth
- F-03 Collect results dashboard  
- F-04 Public template gallery  
- A-02 AI-generated template pages  
- T-02 Instagram Comment Picker (if in scope)  

### Phase 3 — Polish & monetize
- F-05 Embed widget  
- M-01 Premium tier  
- I-01 Discord bot  
- I-02 Mobile  

