## 6. Use-case playbooks (for your classroom / giveaway / exercise ideas)

### Classroom — random student picker
- **Tool:** Main wheel or Team Picker  
- **Mode:** Elimination (don’t repeat until everyone picked)  
- **Competitor gap to close:** Share link for substitute teacher; Collect results optional  
- **Our edge:** Game modes (bingo, memory) for engagement  

### Giveaway — prize categories
- **Tool:** Main wheel with weighted slices OR specialized categories  
- **Competitor:** PickerWheel Collect Results + Instagram Comment Picker  
- **Our gap:** F-03 collect dashboard, T-02 Instagram tool  
- **Our edge:** AI to generate prize list from prompt  

### Daily exercise routine
- **Tool:** Main wheel or Date/Number tools  
- **Mode:** Normal or Accumulation (PickerWheel style — spin multiple times, count wins)  
- **Our gap:** F-22 Accumulation mode, F-04 save routine wheels publicly  
- **Our edge:** AI suggests weekly rotation of exercises  

